  <h1>RED EYES GITHUB BOOTCAMP</h1>
  <p><strong>A scenario-based Git & GitHub learning lab built in Python (Tkinter)</strong></p>

  <p>
    <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.10%2B-blue.svg" alt="Python 3.10+"/>
