  <li>Modular structure: <code>app.py</code>, <code>questions.py</code>, <code>audio.py</code></li>
</ul>

<h2>â–¶ï¸ Run Locally</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Clone the repository:</li>
</ol>
<pre><code>git clone https://github.com/yourusername/red-eyes-github-bootcamp.git
cd red-eyes-github-bootcamp</code></pre>

<ol start="2">
  <li>Run the app:</li>
</ol>
<pre><code>python3 app.py</code></pre>

<p><strong>macOS note:</strong> Use <code>python3</code> (not <code>python</code>).</p>

